<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Peter N., Domherr zu Prag und Pfarrer zu Schlackenwerth</head><p>Der Rat teilt erneut mit, dass kein Nürnberger die Schäden des Adressaten verursacht hat, verweist auf den Rechtsweg und teilt mit, dass ihm weitere Forderungen und Klagen unziemlich erscheinen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_395" id="196v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_395_r1l23">Dem <expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Prag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_395_r1l24">vnd pfarrer ʒu Slakenwerde </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_395_r1l25"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt beuor <expan>l<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Peter als Jr vns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_395_r1l26">von der ſcheden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe eẅch <expan>beſchehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllen ſeyn etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_395_r1l27">haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch vormals ın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_395_r1l28"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchrıfte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> daʒ wır niht fınden noch erfarn </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_396" id="197r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l1"><expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan> ſcheden fürer geweſt ſeyn oder ſchult </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l2"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>lecʒ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brıef <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch von vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l3">vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> freẅntlıche recht / da wır das <expan>pıllıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tun <expan>völlıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l4"><expan>gepotte<ex>n</ex></expan> ob Jr vns ye on ſprüche niht laſſen wolt / <expan>Dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l5">antwurt wır noch nıht wıſſen ʒu endern / wan vns dunkt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l6">daʒ wır eẅch da mit glimpf vnd rechts gnug <expan>gepotte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l7">vnd pıeten / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getrawen wır eẅch Jr . lat eẅch des <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l8">Denn / ob Jr vns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnpıllıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l9">oder ſachen beſweͣrot ſo deẅcht vns / Vns geſchehe daran vngüt = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_396_r1l10">lıch von eẅch / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_395" id="196v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Prag
                        und pfarrer zu Slakenwerde</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor.
                                                  <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Peter, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der
                                                scheden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ewch
                                                  <expan>beschehe<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen seyn
                                                etc., das haben wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch vormals in
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schrifte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz wir niht
                                                finden noch erfarn <pb facs="#facs_396" id="197r"/>
<expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan> scheden fürer gewest
                                                seyn oder schult <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; und
                                                  <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>lecz<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch von uns und
                                                den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> frewntliche
                                                recht, da wir das <expan>pilliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                tun, <expan>völlikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gepotte<ex>n</ex></expan>, ob ir uns ye on
                                                sprüche niht lassen wolt;
                                                  <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> unser antwurt wir
                                                noch niht wissen zu endern, wan uns dunkt, daz wir
                                                ewch da mit glimpf und rechts gnug
                                                  <expan>gepotte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und pieten.
                                                  <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getrawen wir ewch,
                                                ir lat ewch des <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                denn ob ir uns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unpilliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> oder sachen
                                                besweͣrot, so dewcht uns, uns geschehe daran
                                                ungütlich von ewch. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
